
Building
========

The build scripts for Cygwin, Mac OS X and Linux are in the build
directory. Full makefiles to follow soon.


Apache Portable Runtime
=======================

OS specific binaries and includes for APR are found in cygwin/, 
linux/, macosx/ directories.


Source
======

OpenRemote I/O daemon sources and include files are in src/
and include/ directories.


Tests
=====

Run the integration tests from build/ directory (run-integration-test.sh).
You will need to have Java installed for this to work. The Ant tool
used by the script can be found in svn top-level /Tools directory.

